result.title: British Paramount News No.251
result.overview: We Protest: 80,000 descend on Hyde Park to demonstrate against Hitler’s antisemitism.

result.title: Motion Picture: The Kitsune vs. the Tanukis
result.overview: A farmer walking in the woods is frightened away by a shapeshifting fox, who then disguises himself as a samurai and makes his way to a temple, haunted by a young shapeshifting tanuki whose various attempts to frighten the fox/samurai away fail. The young tanuki telephones his father, and they join forces against the samurai.
